
--------------------------------POST------------------------------------
1.Method: createCart Description: It is used to create cart for new user into
   the CART_MODULE table
2. createCart : Method "POST".
3. URL: http://localhost:8085/api/v1/cart/{customerId}
4. INPUT: pass customerId in PathVariable.

-------------------------------GET-----------------------------------------
1.Method:  showAll Description: It is used to fetch all cart details for
   existing user from the CART_MODULE table
2. showAll : Method "GET".
3. URL: http://localhost:8085/api/v1/cart
4. INPUT : not input send request to get all cart Details.

------------------------------DELETE---------------------------------------
1 Method: deleteMedicine Description: It is used to delete specific medicine
	record for existing cart user from the CART_MODULE table
2. deleteMedicine : Method "DELETE".
3. URL: http://localhost:8085/api/v1/cart/{cartId}/{medicineId}
4. INPUT : pass cartId and medicineId in PathVariable

------------------------------DELETE-----------------------------------------
1.Method: deleteMedicines Description: It is used to delete entire cart
   medicines record for existing cart user from the CART_MODULE table
2. deleteMedicines : Method "DELETE". 
3. URL: http://localhost:8085/api/v1/cart/{cartId}
4. INPUT : pass cartId in PathVariable

------------------------------POST-------------------------------------------
1.Method: addToCart Description: It is used to add medicine into cart for new
   or existing user into the CART_MODULE table
2. addToCart : Method "POST".
3. URL: http://localhost:8085/api/v1/cart/addtocart/{customerId}/{medicineId}
4. INPUT : pass customerId and medicineId in PathVariable

------------------------------GET-----------------------------------------------
1.Method: viewMedicines Description: It is used to fetch all medicines details for
    existing user from the CART_MODULE table
2. viewMedicines : Method "GET".
3. URL: http://localhost:8085/api/v1/cart/{cartId}
4. INPUT : pass cartId in PathVariable

-------------------------------GET---------------------------------------------
1.Method: viewCartInfo Description: It is used to fetch cart details for
   existing user from the CART_MODULE table
2. viewCartInfo : Method "GET".
3. URL: http://localhost:8085/api/v1/cart/cartInfo/{cartId}
4. INPUT : pass cartId in PathVariable

------------------------------POST----------------------------------------------
1.Method: addMedicine Description: It is used to add medicine quantity into cart for new
  or existing user into the CART_MODULE table
2. addMedicine : Method "POST".
3. URL: http://localhost:8085/api/v1/cart/{cartId}/{medicineId}/{quantity}
4. INPUT : pass cartId, medicineId and quantity in PathVariable

